<p>
<note n="0848005" resp="#resp2" type="mod" target="#nkr_note_mod_0848005">一卷【大】，〔－〕【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note>
<note n="0848006" resp="#resp2" type="mod" target="#nkr_note_mod_0848006">三藏【大】，唐三藏【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note>
<note n="0848007" resp="#resp2" type="mod" target="#nkr_note_mod_0848007">為【大】，名為【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note>
<note n="0848008" resp="#resp2" type="mod" target="#nkr_note_mod_0848008">串【大】，慣【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note>
<note n="0848009" resp="#resp2" type="mod" target="#nkr_note_mod_0848009">寶【大】＊，實【宋】【元】【宮】＊</note>
<note n="0849001" resp="#resp2" type="mod" target="#nkr_note_mod_0849001">德【大】，得【明】</note>
